p: \bI'm cheering for Mightyena.\nI trained her myself!
\bOh- I mean, go, Mightyena! Make them... faint!

\bIt's technically not allowed above ground, so people try and make some cash here.

\rFor crying out loud, Granbull!\nYou can do better than that!

\rBe careful down here!\nYou can get stuck in that black sludge really easily.
\rIt's a bit dangerous down here, kid.
\rI wouldn't linger too long, just get what you need and go.
An eye stares back at you from the keyhole.
A thin blue liquid seeps from beneath the door.
